## Remediation Priority

### Immediate (within 7 days)

1. Implement prompt hardening — validate all user inputs against adversarial injection patterns before passing to LLM
2. Add a secondary LLM-based output validator to detect policy violations before returning responses
3. Remove all secrets, API keys, and sensitive configuration from system prompts
4. Implement tool call rate limiting and audit logging for all AI-triggered actions
5. Add human-in-the-loop confirmation for all irreversible actions (payments, emails, deletions)

